name: tableful on red_identity crisis
description: "tableful on red" is an analogue collage from the ongoing series "identity crisis" that has begun in the year 2020. this collage consists of an old deconstructed black and white photograph that was found in an abandoned institute of automation in kyiv. this unique collage was cut with a scalpel as if it was jewelry and then glued by Elis / alis la luna in 2021.
